tasks.task: Drive a tractor in corn field
subtasks: Sit in the tractor seat
Operate tractor's steering wheel to navigate through corn field
Use hydraulics to lower or raise implement
Engage gears to move tractor forward or backward
Monitor directions via GPS system

tasks.task: Attach the combine
subtasks: Align the combine with the tractor
Securely attach the combine to the tractor using hitch pins or other fasteners

tasks.task: Drive the combine in the corn field
subtasks: Sit in the combine seat
Use steering wheel to direct the combine through the field
Engage proper speed to maintain efficient harvesting
Monitor combine gauges for performance indicators

tasks.task: Operate the combine to harvest corn
subtasks: Monitor corn ears feeding into the combine
Adjust cutting height as needed
Use controls to open or close the combine's cleaning system
Check grain tank levels periodically

tasks.task: Load grain into the grain truck
subtasks: Stop the combine at the designated unloading location
Open the grain unloading gate
Operate the combine's auger to transfer grain into the truck
Monitor grain flow and ensure proper loading

tasks.task: Unload grain from the grain truck
subtasks: Drive the grain truck to the bin location
Position the truck under the bin's unload chute
Connect the auger from the bin to the truck
Start the unloading process

tasks.task: Drive the grain truck to the grain bin
subtasks: Align the grain truck with the bin's unload chute
Engage proper driving to ensure safe movement
Monitor trailer connections and release when close enough to the bin

tasks.task: Unload grain from the grain truck into the bin
subtasks: Start the auger at the bin to begin unloading
Monitor grain unload rate and adjust as needed
Communicate with combine operator to coordinate loading and unloading timing
- Monitor GPS (SUBTASKS).
- Securily attach using fasteners (SUBTASKS).
- Monitor gauges (SUBTASKS).
- Check grain levels (SUBTASKS).
- Monitor flow (SUBTASKS).
- Start process (SUBTASKS).
- Start auger and manage unload rate (SUBTASKS).
